Description: To save Asgard from a bloodthirsty goddess of death, the mighty Thor will have to battle his way to freedom and find a way back home.
Name: Thor: Ragnarok

Description: Harried fashion entrepreneur Jules gets a surprise boost from Ben, a 70-year-old widower who answers an ad seeking a senior intern.
Name: Intern

Description: After crash-landing on Earth, two royal teen aliens on the run struggle to blend in with humans as they evade intergalactic bounty hunters.
Name: Below

Description: Relegated to the rank of private due to institutional racism in WWII, experienced soldier Edward Carter single-handedly cripples an enemy stronghold.
Name: Metal Of Honor

Description: An optimistic koala tries to save his theater with a singing contest featuring a timid elephant, a teenage gorilla, an overworked sow and more.
Name: Sing

Description: When the Valley of Peace is threatened, lazy Po the panda discovers his destiny as the "chosen one" and trains to become a kung fu hero.
Name: Kung Fu Panda

Description: Growing up with a renowned chef as his idol, Remy the rat develops a taste for fine food. But his culinary ambitions only anger his practical father.
Name: Ratatouille
